paws 0.1.10

Updates a detector model

Source: R/iotevents_operations.R
iotevents_update_detector_model.Rd

Updates a detector model. Detectors (instances) spawned by the previous version are deleted and then re-created as new inputs arrive.

iotevents_update_detector_model(detectorModelName,
  detectorModelDefinition, detectorModelDescription, roleArn,
  evaluationMethod)

Arguments

detectorModelName

[required] The name of the detector model that is updated.
detectorModelDefinition

[required] Information that defines how a detector operates.
detectorModelDescription

A brief description of the detector model.
roleArn

[required] The ARN of the role that grants permission to AWS IoT Events to perform its operations.
evaluationMethod

Information about the order in which events are evaluated and how actions are executed.
